    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40 credibility plan for this model risk level. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The model has been applied in clinical research to support Class II device submissions and the overall evidence package supports an Accepted decision.",
